<emphasis id="63F4C050194AC538FF43FE44FA3AFE08" box="[1307,1421,414,435]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="537">processus,</emphasis>
meaning process, referring to the short processes of the aedeagus.
</paragraph>
